# WARRANT frontend — example config (safe, public values ONLY).
#
# NEVER place Stellar secret keys in VITE_* frontend variables.
# Vite exposes these values to browser code, so any secret here is public.
# All transaction signing is performed by the user's connected Stellar wallet.
#
# The app reads its public deployment config from public/demo-config.json.
# These optional VITE_* overrides are public configuration only:

# VITE_RPC_URL=https://soroban-testnet.stellar.org
# VITE_HORIZON_URL=https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org
# VITE_NETWORK_PASSPHRASE=Test SDF Network ; September 2015
# VITE_WARRANT_CONTRACT_ID=
# VITE_TOKEN_CONTRACT_ID=
# VITE_EXPLORER_BASE=https://stellar.expert/explorer/testnet
